Package: gomailserver
Version: {{VERSION}}
Section: mail
Priority: optional
Architecture: {{ARCH}}
Maintainer: btafoya <btafoya@users.noreply.github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/btafoya/gomailserver
Description: Modern, secure mail server written in Go
 gomailserver is a full-featured mail server implementation that includes:
  * SMTP, IMAP, and POP3 support
  * Web-based administration interface
  * Webmail client
  * CalDAV/CardDAV support
  * DKIM, SPF, and DMARC support
  * Automatic TLS with Let's Encrypt
  * Greylist and anti-spam features
  * PostgreSQL and SQLite support
Depends: ca-certificates, adduser
Recommends: sqlite3
